00:14:34.470 --> 00:14:37.900 align:middle line:84%
I have one on my back and
would be happy to demo it.

00:14:37.900 --> 00:14:38.740 align:middle line:90%
>> Sure.

00:14:38.740 --> 00:14:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>> It is stuck to my
spine, so there it is.

00:14:44.400 --> 00:14:45.200 align:middle line:90%
Yeah?

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:45.590 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:14:45.590 --> 00:14:46.030 align:middle line:90%
>> With the lowest one--

00:14:46.030 --> 00:14:46.575 align:middle line:90%
>> So these electrode--

00:14:46.575 --> 00:14:47.375 align:middle line:90%
>> --on my--

00:14:47.375 --> 00:14:48.190 align:middle line:90%
>> --type things.

00:14:48.190 --> 00:14:48.370 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:14:48.370 --> 00:14:49.190 align:middle line:90%
