00:14:49.190 --> 00:14:49.990 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:14:49.990 --> 00:14:55.670 align:middle line:84%
So the sensors are talking
to our app in real time.

00:14:55.670 --> 00:15:01.570 align:middle line:84%
