00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:23.480 align:middle line:90%
That's not exactly--

00:15:23.480 --> 00:15:24.380 align:middle line:90%
>> A sway back.

00:15:24.380 --> 00:15:25.010 align:middle line:90%
>> A sway.

00:15:25.010 --> 00:15:26.240 align:middle line:84%
>> Or if their tucking
their pelvis and slouching--

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:27.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, pelvis -- they see it.

00:15:27.790 --> 00:15:28.285 align:middle line:90%
>> --too much.

00:15:28.285 --> 00:15:28.570 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:15:28.570 --> 00:15:31.030 align:middle line:10%
>> And then they learn
what it is they need to do

00:15:31.030 --> 00:15:33.560 align:middle line:10%
