00:15:52.400 --> 00:15:53.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:56.390 align:middle line:84%
>> So they take home in
a very visceral way--

00:15:56.390 --> 00:15:57.190 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:57.190 --> 00:16:02.300 align:middle line:84%
>> --why it is that they need
to pay attention to this--

00:16:02.300 --> 00:16:03.100 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:03.100 --> 00:16:04.720 align:middle line:84%
>> --to the shape
of their spine.

00:16:04.720 --> 00:16:07.130 align:middle line:84%
That there are actually
