00:16:07.130 --> 00:16:07.930 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:07.930 --> 00:16:10.960 align:middle line:90%
>> --that merit some attention.

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:12.360 align:middle line:90%
>> Need to be used properly.

00:16:12.360 --> 00:16:13.160 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:17.720 align:middle line:84%
And then gives them
practice in matching targets

00:16:17.720 --> 00:16:20.270 align:middle line:84%
