standing, for bending.

00:16:20.270 --> 00:16:22.040 align:middle line:84%
So this has been
very useful for us

00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:25.430 align:middle line:84%
for helping students learn
more efficiently and also

00:16:25.430 --> 00:16:26.870 align:middle line:90%
for doing research.

00:16:26.870 --> 00:16:29.870 align:middle line:84%
>> Raising consciousness
in the biomechanics.

00:16:29.870 --> 00:16:32.510 align:middle line:84%
And this is inside the
classroom where you teach,

00:16:32.510 --> 00:16:36.120 align:middle line:84%
where you're training people
how to do exactly what we're

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:36.920 align:middle line:90%
talking about.

00:16:36.920 --> 00:16:42.440 align:middle line:84%
>> So most of our teachers
