00:27:39.270 --> 00:27:42.090 align:middle line:84%
You may feel like
you're leaning forward

00:27:42.090 --> 00:27:45.100 align:middle line:84%
because it's so different from
what you were doing previously,

00:27:45.100 --> 00:27:49.560 align:middle line:84%
which was arching back, but
it looks perfectly wonderful.

00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:57.720 align:middle line:84%
And so having a coach encourage
you and guide you to the result

00:27:57.720 --> 00:27:59.200 align:middle line:90%
is the best way.

00:27:59.200 --> 00:28:02.820 align:middle line:84%
And now I have trained over 50
teachers all around the world,

00:28:02.820 --> 00:28:06.450 align:middle line:84%
