this hands on guidance.

00:28:06.450 --> 00:28:08.990 align:middle line:84%
But the book is a really
good starting point,

00:28:08.990 --> 00:28:11.400 align:middle line:90%
It gives a overview.

00:28:11.400 --> 00:28:12.720 align:middle line:90%
It makes sense.

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:15.390 align:middle line:84%
People feel encouraged,
and it starts people

00:28:15.390 --> 00:28:17.970 align:middle line:84%
on the journey with
these easy techniques,

00:28:17.970 --> 00:28:20.790 align:middle line:84%
like stretch sitting
