00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:48.450 align:middle line:84%
>> Esther has already shown
us how to stretch sit.

00:28:48.450 --> 00:28:51.220 align:middle line:84%
Another of the key exercises,
as she's just mentioning,

00:28:51.220 --> 00:28:52.680 align:middle line:90%
