00:33:06.510 --> 00:33:08.940 align:middle line:10%
If I had to give
you three adjectives

00:33:08.940 --> 00:33:12.210 align:middle line:10%
to describe this
work, I would say

00:33:12.210 --> 00:33:16.500 align:middle line:10%
miraculous has to be one,
because you just can't believe

00:33:16.500 --> 00:33:18.840 align:middle line:10%
how much difference it makes.

00:33:18.840 --> 00:33:22.620 align:middle line:10%
Natural is another
one, because it just

00:33:22.620 --> 00:33:26.730 align:middle line:10%
seems the natural way
for the human body to be.

00:33:26.730 --> 00:33:29.200 align:middle line:10%
And easy.

00:33:29.200 --> 00:33:31.320 align:middle line:90%
It's easy to do this.

00:33:31.320 --> 00:33:33.870 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the Gokhale Method
trainers who has facilitated

00:33:33.870 --> 00:33:36.780 align:middle line:84%
some of these remarkable
transformations is actually

00:33:36.780 --> 00:33:40.110 align:middle line:84%
Esther's daughter, Monisha,
and she's joining us here.

00:33:40.110 --> 00:33:41.040 align:middle line:90%
Welcome, Monisha.

00:33:41.040 --> 00:33:41.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:33:41.840 --> 00:33:43.212 align:middle line:90%
>> Wonderful to have you here.

00:33:43.212 --> 00:33:44.670 align:middle line:84%
So you have to tell
us, what was it

00:33:44.670 --> 00:33:47.370 align:middle line:84%
like growing up with
the posture guru?

00:33:47.370 --> 00:33:50.990 align:middle line:84%
>> What it means is that healthy
posture actually came naturally

00:33:50.990 --> 00:33:51.790 align:middle line:90%
to me.

00:33:51.790 --> 00:33:55.590 align:middle line:84%
I was raised in a way that meant
that healthy posture habits

00:33:55.590 --> 00:33:56.910 align:middle line:90%
were part of my everyday life.

00:33:56.910 --> 00:34:01.140 align:middle line:10%
The way she carried me,
the way she adjusted me,

00:34:01.140 --> 00:34:04.620 align:middle line:10%
all led to me approaching
sitting and standing

00:34:04.620 --> 00:34:06.270 align:middle line:10%
and bending and
lying in ways that

00:34:06.270 --> 00:34:09.060 align:middle line:10%
are actually healthy for
my structural integrity.

00:34:09.060 --> 00:34:11.010 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people
think that growing up

00:34:11.010 --> 00:34:12.989 align:middle line:84%
with a posture
teacher as a mother

00:34:12.989 --> 00:34:14.730 align:middle line:84%
might be unpleasant,
because people's

00:34:14.730 --> 00:34:20.280 align:middle line:84%
ideas of healthy posture is
some tense, unpleasant position.

00:34:20.280 --> 00:34:23.820 align:middle line:84%
But, in fact, most of
posture is relaxed.

00:34:23.820 --> 00:34:26.670 align:middle line:84%
And healthy posture
is comfortable.

00:34:26.670 --> 00:34:28.620 align:middle line:84%
>> Did you have good
posture at birth?

00:34:28.620 --> 00:34:29.420 align:middle line:90%
>> I think--

00:34:29.420 --> 00:34:31.980 align:middle line:84%
I think all babies
are actually born

00:34:31.980 --> 00:34:36.150 align:middle line:90%
with natural, healthy alignment.

00:34:36.150 --> 00:34:38.969 align:middle line:84%
And part of the
role of the parent

00:34:38.969 --> 00:34:42.580 align:middle line:84%
is to help maintain those
natural posture habits.

00:34:42.580 --> 00:34:46.440 align:middle line:84%
So yeah, I think all babies are
born with natural alignment.

00:34:46.440 --> 00:34:50.730 align:middle line:84%
And the way Esther
carried me and sat me up

00:34:50.730 --> 00:34:54.600 align:middle line:84%
and held me helped me
maintain a healthy posture

00:34:54.600 --> 00:34:57.400 align:middle line:90%
habits into my adult life.

00:34:57.400 --> 00:35:00.990 align:middle line:84%
>> So how did your education
on correct posture do you--

00:35:00.990 --> 00:35:03.850 align:middle line:84%
how do you feel that it
improved your life experience

00:35:03.850 --> 00:35:04.650 align:middle line:90%
along the way?

00:35:04.650 --> 00:35:08.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, one of the impacts of
having healthy posture habits

00:35:08.670 --> 00:35:12.540 align:middle line:84%
is my expectations on my
musculoskeletal health as I

00:35:12.540 --> 00:35:13.380 align:middle line:90%
age.

00:35:13.380 --> 00:35:15.930 align:middle line:84%
Many people in our culture
see how common back pain

00:35:15.930 --> 00:35:18.990 align:middle line:84%
is and expect that they're going
to have back pain at some point

00:35:18.990 --> 00:35:20.520 align:middle line:90%
if they haven't already.

00:35:20.520 --> 00:35:23.130 align:middle line:84%
I have a lot of
confidence in sitting

00:35:23.130 --> 00:35:26.490 align:middle line:84%
and standing and
bending and being active

00:35:26.490 --> 00:35:29.000 align:middle line:84%
while maintaining
structural integrity,

00:35:29.000 --> 00:35:30.810 align:middle line:84%
and so I don't expect
to have back pain.

00:35:30.810 --> 00:35:34.740 align:middle line:84%
I never have had back issues or
major chronic musculoskeletal

00:35:34.740 --> 00:35:38.040 align:middle line:84%
issues, and I don't expect
to develop those as I age.

00:35:38.040 --> 00:35:39.660 align:middle line:84%
Another really
important thing for me

00:35:39.660 --> 00:35:42.248 align:middle line:84%
is its impact on my
life as an athlete.

00:35:42.248 --> 00:35:44.040 align:middle line:84%
Being an athlete is
really important to me.

00:35:44.040 --> 00:35:46.170 align:middle line:90%
It's a big part of who I am.

00:35:46.170 --> 00:35:51.510 align:middle line:10%
And having healthy posture
has, one, improved performance.

00:35:51.510 --> 00:35:54.780 align:middle line:84%
Good form and good posture
is a really big piece

00:35:54.780 --> 00:36:00.480 align:middle line:84%
of being an effective athlete,
and also on injury prevention

00:36:00.480 --> 00:36:04.980 align:middle line:84%
as well as when injuries
do happen, injury recovery.

00:36:04.980 --> 00:36:09.240 align:middle line:84%
>> So how and when did you
decide to become involved with

00:36:09.240 --> 00:36:11.130 align:middle line:90%
the Gokhale Method?

00:36:11.130 --> 00:36:13.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Informally, I would say I've
been involved since before I

00:36:13.830 --> 00:36:16.120 align:middle line:90%
was born and since birth.

00:36:16.120 --> 00:36:16.920 align:middle line:90%
But formally--

00:36:16.920 --> 00:36:18.410 align:middle line:84%
>> It's kind of a
no-choice choice?

00:36:18.410 --> 00:36:19.210 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:36:19.210 --> 00:36:21.000 align:middle line:84%
I've been raised
in a way that means

00:36:21.000 --> 00:36:24.990 align:middle line:84%
that I've been implementing a
lot of healthy posture habits

00:36:24.990 --> 00:36:28.410 align:middle line:84%
even before I knew
formally or in an educated

00:36:28.410 --> 00:36:31.050 align:middle line:90%
